{"tid":2107020,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"塗緊申我黎話你聽你衰乜，建議你明哲保身","createTime":"2020-07-13T15:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T15:20:40.000Z","uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be26e2dbff30ecf7e81d3416e7533e6a186c6494","tid":2107020,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:03:33.000Z","msg":"初選論壇你問選民你仲有冇資格留番係土議會<br />\n結果話你聽你冇<br />\n你問點解？<br />\n我黎話你聽<br />\n<br />\n1. 初選論壇有人問題點解冇乜係示威現場現身：<br />\n你夠膽死直認自己走唔郁係負累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話你會企係土後方等人whatsapps你<br />\n可見你<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">完全不掌握</span></span>選民而家對議員既期望<br />\n<br />\n2. 我係中国人呀屌：<br />\n不解釋，你估10年前咩<br />\n就算老泛民都唔buy呢套講到出口既大中華膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 議員資歷：<br />\n奶共已經破左你局，你個身份仲有乜價值<br />\n以後唔會再有選主席拉布既可能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論係選民話你知已經out撚晒，衝又唔得<br />\n勸你明哲保身，自動退落黎係其他崗位繼續抗爭<br />\n咪學哥基、白頭忠咁落台落得咁難睇"},{"pid":"728e99d5c01bb59626e2c5e4db19c9ba458385e1","tid":2107020,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"超區出四個去選 wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2677510617f037256177f0d8a658c7e46570f108","tid":2107020,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"728e99d5c01bb59626e2c5e4db19c9ba458385e1","tid":2107020,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"超區出四個去選 wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"應該最後三個，一個後補"},{"pid":"fa600beb1a7c9144b7e7c71652f9f857e92a8322","tid":2107020,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"728e99d5c01bb59626e2c5e4db19c9ba458385e1","tid":2107020,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":1,